  "detailed_description": "Run For Your Life is survival Roguelite game being solo-developed by Puke&Guts, where you:<br>-only have melee weapons<br>-aren't very good at combat<br>-are a potato<br><br><i>And it's extremely fun!</i><br>Armed only with a baseball bat, you'll need to be creative- <strong>Set Traps, Lure Hordes & Barricade Rooms</strong> while you wait to progress.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383490/extras/84a91db03c37497f5749e2f9199e4b49.poster.avif?t=1706028011\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383490/extras/84a91db03c37497f5749e2f9199e4b49.webm?t=1706028011\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383490/extras/84a91db03c37497f5749e2f9199e4b49.mp4?t=1706028011\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>Every object can be moved and destroyed, and even repaired with the right upgrades.</i><br><br>You will have the opportunity to upgrade from the standard bat though!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383490/extras/09714692473dcaff042caf13f35020ea.poster.avif?t=1706028011\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383490/extras/09714692473dcaff042caf13f35020ea.webm?t=1706028011\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383490/extras/09714692473dcaff042caf13f35020ea.mp4?t=1706028011\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>Every level begins with a choice of<strong> Weapon, Ability or Passive Upgrade</strong> to spice up your run.</i><br><br>Just because your weapons are melee does NOT mean no ranged combat!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383490/extras/d8945e31ccf8e2598113add62dcc991f.poster.avif?t=1706028011\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383490/extras/d8945e31ccf8e2598113add62dcc991f.webm?t=1706028011\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383490/extras/d8945e31ccf8e2598113add62dcc991f.mp4?t=1706028011\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>Use smaller objects as <strong>Improvised Weapons and Projectiles.</strong> Send a chair flying into a crowd, instant chaos.</i><br><br>Tons of Unique Worlds with New Mechanics Incoming<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383490/extras/0ae33655b4edd89bccc924c157776a0d.poster.avif?t=1706028011\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383490/extras/0ae33655b4edd89bccc924c157776a0d.webm?t=1706028011\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383490/extras/0ae33655b4edd89bccc924c157776a0d.mp4?t=1706028011\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>The level list is small to start, but should offer a glimpse of the future and potential of Run For Your Life!</i>",
